com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport

Class ItemDiscriminator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport.ItemDiscriminator

  • public final class ItemDiscriminator
extends Object
    A means of characterizing an Item that is used for determining whether other Items of the same ItemType are duplicates.

      Gets a String containing the identifier of the ItemType that this ItemDiscriminator applies to.
